    "Yet, as a technology that is both \"transformative\" and \"disruptive,\" its future development demands a nuanced understanding of its current applications and the untapped potential it holds (McCormack, 2023; Robert, 2024).",
    "Since late 2022, researchers and practitioners have increasingly integrated GenAI into their teaching and learning, leading to a rapid increase in studies on its applications.",
